" vim-easy-align {
" For visual mode (e.g. vip<Enter>)
vmap <Enter>   <Plug>(EasyAlign)

" For normal mode, with Vim movement (e.g. <Leader>aip)
nmap <Leader>a <Plug>(EasyAlign)

" Repeat alignment in visual mode with . key
vmap . <Plug>(EasyAlignRepeat)
" }
